snippet.title: Coral: A Halo Fan Game | June Update
snippet.description:
This month has been hugely focused on building our team and getting the groundwork laid out for the progress that is to come. Stay tuned for next month, we've got a lot of work coming down the pipeline that you won't want to miss!

Sign up for Coral Dev Team: https://bit.ly/joincoralteam

Our New Members:
-  HALOGEN117 - 3D Modeler
-  Kyle Booth - Composer
-  Mixer - Story Writer
-  Sperdunky - Level Designer

---------
Instagram: @coralgame
Discord: https://discord.gg/KEPgcvH
YouTube: Coral: A Halo Fan Game
---------
Follow us individually:
Austin - Lead Community Manager: @halo_shitposts on Instagram
Nathan - Lead Developer: @officialjebobs on Twitter
